data.description: Welcome home! A perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this stunning single-family home in picturesque Tehaleh. Enjoy the lifestyle in a neighborhood surrounded by stunning nature and top-notch amenities. With a spacious layout and modern features, this home boasts 3-bed, 2.5-bath,  a spacious kitchen with a panoramic view of the main floor—overlooking an elegant dining room & large great room. Spacious owner's suite complete with large walk in closet, loft & 2 additional bedrooms upstairs. Has a great backyard space for entertaining and outdoor activities. Located next to trailhead for easy access to over 30+ miles of hiking trails and parks. Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity to make it yours! ASK ABOUT ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE
